    • Constructor Detail

      • Reservation

        public Reservation​(int CAMP_SITE_ID,
                   DateRange DATE_RANGE)
        Constructor for the reservation we are making. We can still make a reservation if it already exists or is overlapping, but we cannot put it in the reservation store. This functionality is for future considerations, such as creating wait lists for a campsite time (consider cancellations as a possible cause for this feature).
        Parameters:
        CAMP_SITE_ID - the ID associated with the campsite we are making a reservation for.
        DATE_RANGE - the date range to make the reservation on.
